         <ttm:title>Permanent Price Reduction (Industry Partner requested)</ttm:title>
         <ttm:desc>A Permanent Price Reduction Modification may also be implemented for the purposes of lowering costs through an Industry Partnership, in which case an &quot;Industry Partner Request&quot; is added to the Schedule Contract.
         </ttm:desc>
      </metadata>
