   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:02.03" end="00:00:04.30" region="speaker">Here you can set a Permanent Price Reduction</p>
         <p begin="00:00:04.30" end="00:00:06.73" region="speaker">for your contract as requested by an Industry</p>
         <p begin="00:00:06.73" end="00:00:07.93" region="speaker">Partner.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:07.93" end="00:00:10.56" region="speaker">As this modification could potentially impact your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:10.56" end="00:00:12.80" region="speaker">projections of how much business you plan to do</p>
         <p begin="00:00:12.80" end="00:00:14.73" region="speaker">with the government, you may need to review and</p>
         <p begin="00:00:14.73" end="00:00:18.06" region="speaker">update your Commercial Sales Practice If so,</p>
         <p begin="00:00:18.06" end="00:00:20.73" region="speaker">click Yes and Save, upon which you will be taken</p>
         <p begin="00:00:20.73" end="00:00:22.86" region="speaker">through the CSP utility.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:22.86" end="00:00:25.53" region="speaker">Updating your CSP is covered in a different</p>
         <p begin="00:00:25.53" end="00:00:26.63" region="speaker">video.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:26.63" end="00:00:30.10" region="speaker">If this is not the case, select No and continue</p>
         <p begin="00:00:30.10" end="00:00:33.40" region="speaker">with the modification First select a &quot;Start</p>
         <p begin="00:00:33.40" end="00:00:35.40" region="speaker">Date&quot; for your Permanent Price Reduction.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:37.56" end="00:00:39.43" region="speaker">Enter a description detailing your price</p>
         <p begin="00:00:39.43" end="00:00:41.63" region="speaker">reduction including information such as the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:41.63" end="00:00:45.93" region="speaker">requesting entity and the reason for the reduction.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:45.93" end="00:00:47.66" region="speaker">When you are finished click the &quot;Save and</p>
         <p begin="00:00:47.66" end="00:00:49.66" region="speaker">Continue&quot; button.</p>
    </div>
